## Key entities

```hopscotch:npc id=npc.leader.seran-holt
name: Seran Holt
scope: location.brinehook-hamlet
alignment: NG
ancestry: elf
role: community leader
statblock: "veteran (variant)"
hooks:
  - "Wants discreet help; fears panic."
knows:
  - secret.second-victim
  - secret.origin.vials
```

```hopscotch:secret id=secret.second-victim
name: Another villager shows the blue-vein symptom
scope: location.brinehook-hamlet
text: >
  Seran has seen the same cold-blue veins on a trapper who refuses help and wants to be left alone.
reveal:
  - by: npc.leader.seran-holt
    method: conversation
```

```hopscotch:check id=check.eldens-footprints
skill: Investigation
dc: 12
onSuccess: "Find bootprints leading toward the reluctant trapper’s cabin."
onFail: "You learn only that someone searched the cabin recently."
```

```hopscotch:secret id=secret.origin.vials
name: Cracked blue vials carry a freezing spore
scope: region.rimewild-frontier
text: >
  The “blue glass” is not glass alone; a dust inside the vial spreads a freezing sickness when exposed.
leadsTo:
  - area.brinehook.curio-nook
  - location.coldjaw-caverns
```

```hopscotch:hazard id=hazard.coldjaw.frigid-pool
name: Frigid Pool Exhaustion
scope: area.coldjaw.c1
trigger: "A creature becomes fully submerged."
effect: "DC 10 Con save or gain 1 level of exhaustion; repeat each minute submerged."
```

```hopscotch:clock id=clock.frostbound-blight
name: Frostbound Blight Progression
scope: region.rimewild-frontier
unit: days
tracks:
  - subject: "Merchant family"
    max: 60
    milestones:
      - at: 30
        effect: "Symptoms worsen; movement slows."
      - at: 60
        effect: "Death."
  - subject: "Cavern boss"
    max: 30
  - subject: "Reluctant trapper"
    max: 20
```

