## Encounters

```hopscotch:encounter id=encounter.elro.plea
name: Seran’s Plea for Help
scope: area.brinehook.graveyard
encounterType: social
trigger: "After the funeral scene."
participants:
  - ref: npc.leader.seran-holt
notes: "Seran offers 100 gp for answers and emphasizes urgency."
```

```hopscotch:encounter id=encounter.cabin.search
name: Search Elden’s Cabin
scope: area.brinehook.eldens-cabin
encounterType: exploration
trigger: "Characters investigate the cabin."
checks:
  - skill: Investigation
    dc: 12
    onSuccess: secret.origin.vials
    onFail: "You find signs of a frantic search but no clear lead."
```

```hopscotch:encounter id=encounter.shop.raiders
name: Raiders in the Curio Nook
scope: area.brinehook.curio-nook
encounterType: combat
trigger: "Characters enter the shop or are noticed."
participants:
  - ref: srd:bandit
    count: 5
rewards:
  - loot.orders-to-caves
```

```hopscotch:loot id=loot.orders-to-caves
name: Orders pointing to Coldjaw Caverns
scope: area.brinehook.curio-nook
items:
  - name: "Crumpled orders"
    kind: "clue"
    value: 0
    text: "A note references a hideout north on the frozen shore and mentions the boss is “getting slow.”"
```

```hopscotch:encounter id=encounter.coldjaw.pool-guardians
name: Pool Guardians
scope: area.coldjaw.c1
encounterType: combat
trigger: "Approach within 5 feet of the pool if guardians are hidden."
participants:
  - ref: creature.coldjaw.ice-frog
    count: 2
notes: "Each fights to half HP, then flees into the water."
```

```hopscotch:encounter id=encounter.coldjaw.boss
name: Boss Chamber Confrontation
scope: area.coldjaw.c6
encounterType: mixed
trigger: "Characters enter the chamber."
participants:
  - ref: creature.boss.xyz
    count: 1
choices:
  - text: "Attempt negotiation"
    outcome: "Boss demands proof of help; may buy time."
  - text: "Fight"
    outcome: "Combat begins."
escalation:
  advanceClock:
    id: clock.frostbound-blight
    amount: 1
```

